data.title: Chapter 3:Coop Calls Spencer about Olivia

data.text:
(A Few Minuets after Olivia leaves)

Coop's POV: I frown softly as I watch Olivia and that old Dealer and user Tj drive off. What is she doing with him? I look at the pictures of them kissing that I took and think of what I heard. How do they even know each other? Tj was in some bougie Rehab and then came back with his baby girl. I sigh as I call Spencer. He picks up .

*Phone Call*

Spencer:"what up coop?" I sigh softly

Me:"Hey S,I jut saw Olivia hear. "

Spencer:"Olivia? She just texted Layla that she had to meet with her sponsor." I think a little and then remember the small tattoo shop they left. Ohhh right! some ex-addicts are sponsors.

Me:"she met with her but she didn't leave with her . Remember Tj from grade school?" I can basically hear him rolling his eyes. Tj was one of Shawns boys. One we grew up with .

Spencer:"why you talking about that fool? He don't got nothing to do with Olivia." I frown softly as I remember how close they seemed.

Me:"Actually I just saw those two together. You know me I'm not gonna step in no one's business. But it's weird Spence! They kissed and said something about old habits dying hard." I explain Something's off about those two they keeping secrets." I know it.

Spencer:"Kissed? Old habits? " I nod my head before remembering something.

Me:" wait wasn't Tj's rehab somewhere in Beverly?" I ask Spencer sighs softly

Spencer:" i'll look into it . I'm starting to see your point somethings not right here. How Olivia would Olivia know Tj so well?" I try to hold back my theory knowing TJ because I've met his daughter. He has a baby girl.

Me:"well.... I have a thought." I Say chuckling nervously.

Spencer:" what is it coop?"

Me:" TJ had a baby girl with someone girlfriend of his when they where in rehab. That baby is light skin and she's just a shade over Olivia and Jordan. And that baby is about to be one in three months." I explain hoping dates don't add up!

Spencer:" if they were in rehab together it's Possible Jordan said Olivia was in there for an entire year when everyone expected her to be out in unless six months."

Me:" you Gotta be kidding me I got to go I'll call you later!" I Say before ending the call
